NOTEPAD IS A UTILITY FOR SAVINGNOTES.  RUN 'NOTEPAD'; TYPE YOURMESSAGE; AND   PRESS CTRL-D WHENYOU'RE READY TO SAVE  IT.  THENENTER A FILENAME.  BLOAD IT   LATERTO RESTORE IT.NOTE: THIS UTILITY MAY HAVEUNEXPECTED  SIDE EFFECTS WHEN USEDWITH CERTAIN     PERIPHERAL DEVICESCONNECTED; AS IT     READS ANDWRITES THE 'SCREEN HOLES' WHENNOTESARE LOADED AND SAVED.